content: i have brought items using this app and the app works well very easy to find what you are looking for they have a huge variety of items and prices are good free shipping can be slow if you dont want to pay for shipping but all in all the app is great i enjoy using it update i have recently notice that some sellers are showing an item with a low price but when you go to puchase it it is not that item it is a different item for the lower price and the item you wanted cost more unfair

its a really great service ive gotten decent quality items in the past its easy to use however my issue is the shippingshipping times a lot of times i check the shipping on the items i order and it says its in my city yet the next day i check it says it hasnt even been sorted in the sorting centers aliexpress would be top tier if they fixed this small issue because quite frankly im tired of checking the mail every single morning just to be disappointed

i have to remove the app to be able to order from the website otherwise website takes me back to the app because the app isnt working for me besides there are multiple issues with the app as i cant see the buy 3 items to get free delivery and so many other things that are not working on the app not to mention the search menu is not showing what i really am searching for i wish you would fix the appso i can rate it at 5 because so far i love shopping at aliexpress

ive been using aliexpress for a few years now with much success buying good quality products and saving money shipping times have always been outstanding if an issue with a product i ordered ever came up it was resolved in a timely fashion overall i have no complaints about using the aliexpress app and can definitely recommend anyone to use it

i did almost all of my online shopping on my laptop for ages over the last few years ive started using phone apps this one is pretty good they have made many improvements over time really good sales pop up from time to time there are several games built in for winning discount coins overall its a pretty decent experience personally i keep the notifications off so that i dont get bombarded with annoying ads constantly

you may or may not receive your order if you do not be prepared to jump through months of hoops to try to get a refund the only dispute process is to call the courier that never received the item and get them to certify non receipt very shady in bait and switch pricing too an item will list at one price but its actually another price but posted with an entirely different item that is the first price shady all around

ive reviewed this shopping app before and gave it one star at the time everything was going wrong i was getting items that didnt last theyd break under the lightest usage conditions and i could not get a resolution on a credit that was owed to me i had to go through my bio and lo and behold i got not only the 50 credit they offered me i got a total refund back into my bank account since then ive still been shopping on this site and have bought a lot of items ive had positive results

products are excellent however cancelling orders is difficult and laborious substantial discounts did not get applied to the orders as promised by ae and any further orders had to be held up this is very distressing and will cause problems for the whole months purchases tracking is becoming an issue the product has been delivered and is excellent the closing process does need to be improved a little bit to make accidents less likely more like the reviews where each item is checked off

love how all of the products are very reasonably priced but you definitely have to read the description on each product because some of the items are misleading and you think your getting one thing when its something totally different like a comforter set and all you get is the comforter shell sheet also it takes forever for some of the products to be delivered while some of them are delivered within a week but i guess its worth it when your paying way less than what you would anywhere else

the app works fine i can find stuff on aliexpress that is unique and i cant get on temu or wish i dont like it that a seller will post a cheap price on an item then charge a lot for shipping or that price is only for one size and its more for a different size i think thats dishonest its a good app and they have good prices but sometimes it says itll be 2 months before its delivered so you have to be careful when you order

you get what you pay for ive ordered quite a few things from them some good some not so good good luck getting a refund in case anything goes wrong ive had items missing from orders and issues with items not being as advertised and the amount of hoops you have to jump through and proof you need to provide to get a refund is ridiculous 95 of the time aliexpress sides with the sellers regardless

the cart system is very odd it doesnt show you what you actually have selected first so you have to scroll to even find it and it bugs so its not there the wishlist has a limit and the cart has a limit too so you can never save as many items as you want amazon never has this issue so idk why they chose to do this the my picks cart for the discount items bugs so you cant click anything slow loading times etc its good but boy is this app bugged all to heck

overall the app and the service are very good the only thing that drives me crazy is the regularly popup advertising windows sometimes without the ability to close without clicking on them or x is very well hidden this behavior reminds me of lowgrade sites with viral or aggressive advertising which is disgusting

some stuff takes a while to get but all and all its a great app i enjoy getting stuff in the mail and i like to look good too this app as well as a couple others keep my mailbox full and always something new to try and wear one thing to watch is that the prices are low but you may have a high shipping price this usually helps in the long run you arent charged tax for shipping prices are still lower than local stores and have prices close to shein and temu

their cancel account feature is just for show tried everything i could but they just make you jump through hoops only to make the cancel button in the finalization page unavailable had to make a whole new email so i wouldnt have to see their ads on my main email also if you tried to disable the feature that gives you email ads it gives you the same problem as the account cancelation where theyll straight up not let you

the application is very deceptive platformance designed for people looking to scam you be aware of what youre adding to your cart because while an item may look like like a good deal you need to watch for bait and switch items it might not be what you think always check your shipping there are shops that like to sell items for 100 with 2000 in shipping be aware most electronics you get will either be counterfeit or not work aliexpress as a whole doesnt care they enable it all

love the low prices but the app is annoying the advertisements that pop up on my phone even when im not using the app are aweful makes it seem like my phone has a virus also i find it very annoying that you can not access anything from the home page and you have to click through the choice items before you can see your cart or account information bleh sucks

overall the app itself is ok a little confusing to navigate at first if you dont know where to look for certain things such as your recent purchases on bottom row account then near the top view all im still unsure about how to obtain and redeem coupons coins and other bonuses refunds and returns are easy enough although depending on the item a return isnt always required to obtain a refund 08232023 unable to update app no details given just wont update

im starting to get the pop up ad or screen page glitch every few seconds it looks exactly like the one that has the orange button once tap on the screenandgoes to the login screen with different login apps its starting to get really annoying when trying to read the descriptions and browsing through the products please fix this annoying pop up error glitch it does make me frustrated and dont feel like getting on aliexpress app

if youre able to spend the time to research and compare products to one another you can clearly see the killer deals on things thatd you would normally pay 23 times more for on other shopping apps ive ordered about 20 items give or take items ranging between 099to180 and ive never had any bad or questionable experiences and the things that i ordered more often than not arrived being much high quality than i was expecting by looking at the photos on the site id recommend

tried to return a pair of shoes that were too small and aliexpress refused to provide a return label or refund i even repurchased the new size and paid for it in full but they didnt care to do right by me on the original pair despite the fact that i spent over 1000 usd in the last month unfortunately ill be ordering a lot less from them moving forward if they want to grow they should learn from amazon oh and their app and algorithm needs drastic improvement

love the products on this app buy from here all the time but the problem is with the site itself it is so frustrating and annoying half the time it freezes up and wont work and the other half of the time it refreshes or goes all way back to home page when you hit go back button i really wish they would fix this cuz when you hit back button you lose your place and it sends you all the way back to home page and refreshes i hate it please fix this

so far ive had no bad experience with ali express in fact i kinda love this app very much checking out can be kind of confusing though just make sure you thoroughly read the description and do research before purchasing otherwise you cant help but enjoy browsing i end up with a cart load every time dont forget to use store coupons when available

it is very invasive relentless texts and emails and ads displaying my purchases with no regard for privacy add to cart can be sketchy funny if you click buy it now that works just fine there are also some weird restrictions on what can ship to the us one product may ship just fine yet an identical one wont ship to the us im still trying to figure that out watch shipping costs very carefully sneaky ones lurk out there 20 for a walmart camping cart and 480 shipping

i shop quite a bit with the aliexpress app it takes a learning curve to understand how to find specific items but once you learn it becomes easy i know they serve a lot of languages and translation from chinese dilects to english is difficult i do wish they would invest more resources on this issue but it is not a showstopper overall i do applaud them for a really good app and great product selection i enjoy using the app and i like doing business with aliexpress

the worst customer service ph numbers dont work 24customer service is a joke and after the transaction i only received a payment confirmation from paypal but none from aliexpress not even a tracking update ill stick with temu you can call them anytime refunds are super easy and most of the time you can request it to be just put back in the temu credit which takes 3 minutes many times its not worth it to temu to return the item so you keep or throw it away easy

ive used it a lot now unfortunately with times like they are its become more my go to than amazon if you save the image of a product you saw on amazon and look for it in the search on aliexpress you will probably find it and it will be much cheaper in the case of a desk chair its hundreds cheaper also i ordered some hand painted wallpaper from aliexpress for about 1k and it did arrive and it was exactly what they advertised honestly most of the products on other apps can be found there

the app gets better over time its really easy to order and keeo track of orders within the app cons searches should be exact in this day in age results are very very inaccurate if you have the words in the wrong order your results are completely different this leads me to believe its intentional either that or its poor programming please have an accurate search feature i can not ask a question to a seller i have tried in every version and it gives me an error

i had not dealt with them before so i really liked the prices they are for 95 of the time definitely the best prices and ive had nothing but extremely great experiences with them i highly recommend to anyone that if you are looking for a really good quality performance or durable itemthis is definitely where to go not only are the prices amazing but they litterly have everything imaginable if you havent shopped here than you are really missing out my recommendation 100

it is very good but has some serious downsides seems that most sellers publish not their own item photos and so you can receive something that looks entirely different usually you can get refunds but not always and that is seriously bad the color shades are wrong almost always and its just frustrating another big downside is all the plastic of deliveries yet overall a real important app offering such a huge variety

ive been using this app since last 10 years and overall its been a decent experience the prices are competitive and ive successfully ordered multiple products through it however i must mention that the delivery times seem longer compared to other international ecommerce platforms ive used it would be great if they could enhance delivery speed and tracking reliability

not liking the new cart update its confusing to see the stuff i just added to my cart down at the bottom as if they were added weeks ago i cant keep my stuff organized or pick through them without going through the entire list please bring back chronological order for the cart they seem to be organized by who its shipped by now and thats nice and all but it makes organization confusing go back to organizing by seller and when it was added it cart

search function has been modified to show dozens of completely unrelated items after the first dozen or so results making it borderline useless finding specific items is now harder when i have to sift through 75 unrelated ads causing me to close the app and find what im looking for on ebay users will tolerate a bit of advertising but not at this reduction of function i like the shops i can find via aliexpress but ill be taking a break until this is fixed

the navigation is not good sometimes is difficult to navigate between pages and always you lost where you were previously there are many products that are showing with a lower price but when you open the product page is another item the item shown in the photo is more expensive there are some issues with refund im having an issue with a seller that are trying to use the bugs from the plataform to get money from me ive contacted twice the chat but they didnt tried to solve

when to buy some stuff during the last hours of the 1111 event sale it was advertising for every 25 get 5 back up to 20 i bought 100 worth of items but they only gave me 5 off cancel half the order to rebuy it to get the discount the funds never showed up in my coupons even though it said it would be processed in seconds went to check out with the items and it didnt apply any discount i think the app just swallowed 50

product selection is confusing i tried for a few months but found tracking was inaccurate and terrible a number of items took 2 months to aust 2 never arrived customer service both from aliexpress and many sellers is terrible god help u if u have an issue one item sent on 24th dec tracked upto the 28th as still on china 6 weeks i asked for refund andwer no they rechecked tracking and found it was last tracked to russia and they simply said it was still on its way to australia

the last update is worse than the previous version i used to experience some glitches in the language as it switches every now and then i hoped itd be solved by the new update however its only gotten worse for now i have to switch it back and forth manually yes i live in an arabic speaking country but i want the apps ui language to be english for better ux because of the bad enar translation also whenever i click on a super deals item it takes me to a webpage solve this please

some merchants takes forever to send out stuff when you want to cancel its impossible then when there is an issue with the delivery aliexpress just denies it you can make a complaint but nothing comes out of it and its almost impossible to get any refund out of it so you are welcome for the donation for a useless support system

its nice and the user interface is quite neat but i wan na make a suggestion the coins that we get are only used for discounts obviously but i was just thinking if you can make the coins earning a challenge and ppl can actually buy stuffs with the coin this is my first time using aliexpress this is just a suggestion and its left to your team to decide thanks

i have noticed over the last two three years at the aliexpress app has continued to evolve and improve the app responds quicker and i find it very quick to shop for items on aliexpress without a doubt the shipping times are not just accurate but i would say 6070 of the time my packages will arrive before the eta quicker many times than amazon ebay is a disaster because the shipping methods and address mistakes can double their shipping times aliexpress continues to impress me every day

this app makes it hard to sort items and has tiny images of the product you select making it hard to actually know until again clicking elsewhere to see large images in your cart needs to be a more responsive design prices listed are hardly ever your final cost annoying there is no option to only show you costs with shipping added in when following ads from emails to the ap the prices are always higher the rating system is set up to pay people with points so its totally irrelevant

watch out for false prices i placed an order for an item which was a good price seller never shipped item got my money back but then notices the price had doubled so they didnt want to sell it to me at the original price ordered the same item from someone else and its happening again cheap stuff is fine expensive stuff be careful for gouging

i have no issue with it the problem is with vendors claiming to be located in and shipping from the us i have ordered the same item from two different vendors claiming to be located in the us and able to expedite my shipment via fedex they charge my credit card and never ship the order they dont say anything or string me along until the shipping deadline expires and the order automatically cancels getting a refund is a nightmare dont trust them vendors are in china and reply late

so far this app has a dysfunctional interface to try to get to review an item takes multiple steps and to go back to your profile after requires navigating forward not backward which is unusual its easier to use on my pc it gets confusing lumping parts and sets of products together as 1 listing i thought i was ordering a set because the price was lower when in fact they are individual parts i have not gotten the promotional price of anything yet for being a first time userdeceiving

the app is easy to use placing orders is quick and easy except for some sellers putting low prices on items that is not directly related to the picture you to click to find out what exactly is being sold that is time consuming they will show a picture of a nice camera or watch for a very low price and when take your time to confirm the product only to find theyre selling a battery for that camera or watch then the price change when u click again on the product user friendly app

i personally really like this app and use it all the time when buying stuff it has low prices and everything when buying something though i always check the reviews first just to see because sometimes they might come different than the image so its always best i have a lot of coins on the app but they rarely do anything i would recommend this app to friends and family as i like it a lot shipping sometimes takes quite a while but its always worth it

ive had success with all of my purchases however the site itself will inundate you with messages with coupons from sellers you never even looked at the messages arent from the sellers themselves but the site auto sending them its incredibly annoying and creates issues with the seller if they piss off their customers as i said ive had good experiences with the sellers but be prepared for aliexpress to send you messages all day the refund option is convoluted and unnecessary

been using this app for about a month now and made a couple of purchases as well nothing much to complain but i have a small concern usually a product having different types are displayed with the image of the highest priced type and the cost of the lowest one i click on these with excitement only to be disappointed with the actual price

the customer service sucks there is a chance your order is wrong missing or broken if this happens aliexpress will always take the sellers side and not give a refund their excuse is always that the evidence provided isnt valid then they give you the option to send the item you bought back for a refund but you have to cover the shipping yourself sometimes the shipping price is more than the price of the product itself

unfortunately the option to have multiple prices for each listing has made this app wildly inaccurate and pretty unusable you click on something for five euro when you go into the listing you see that its not the item you searched for instead its some irrelevant washer or something and the item you searched for is in the same listing but its about sixty euro just an update its even worse now no matter what you search for youll have no results that match just ads

app is great easy to find items favouriting makes it much easier to go back to something youre interested in and want to keep an eye on for a better deal way too many push notifications everything youve looked at you end up getting push notification for it

i have been using aliexpress for a few years now if everything is ok then its good if you have not received the product then aliexpress confirms that the item has been received on your behalf automatically after 84 days no matter how many times you say that upu have not received the product the customer service is like a parrot keep repeating the same thing again and again they don ’ t understand english very well i am planning to uninstall this app and go fir well known app a

full of bugs forms covered with phone keyboard with no way to tab down collect coins but absolutely no way of using them to buy things annoying ad on startup which counts down floating button gets in the way bottom buttons cart etc disappear so no way of navigating so many fake itemsreviews its like being on trustpilot

great app i use it all the time but needs a bug fix or else its intentional its quite invasive it pops up and takes over google search results and at other times i deinstalled it once and am not sure its entirely fixed after the lenovo info harvesting debacle this makes me nervous

it is good to order from if you want something cheap but dont by something expensive thats a risk the app itself is getting corrupt in the way that its getting buggy ive experienced it being in inverted colors for a long time now and there is just too much pop up ads

largely easy to find stuff on the app it might be helpful to add an option to navigate to picks from the cart icon if you have active picks and have to leave for any reason it can be hard to return and finish

the app is infested with unwanted popups coupon scams and misleading promotions most sellers are untrustworthy the products are junk and theres no support because the site and sellers are all savvy to the tricks necessary to game the system if you have any complaints or problems with an order they just ban you they only accept credit cards so your only option in case of fraud is a chargeback theres nothing they sell that is worth the hassle of dealing with deceptive overseas sellers

this app is a scam dont trust it it is a huge hit or miss with these sellers yes you may recieve some of your items however sellers will send you disturbing items that is nothing like what you ordered or you just wont recieve your item at all trying to dispute it is useless dont count on getting your money back also be cautious bc in order to file a dispute the app wants access to your audio now why on earth would they need that there are other apps more reliable dont waste

the app is very helpful all the products ive bought so far are of good quality and delivery has been earlier than expected apart from 1 item however some product sellers need to give more accurate description eg some school bags dont have any measure further more i would love to be able to buy different varietiescolors for a particular product in a single order

i loved this app used it all the time until they decided to block all payment options and demand everything from my drivers license to bank statements absolutely not shady af and screams scam central no other shopping app has ever asked for anything like that theres not even a notification that they blocked anything until you go to pay customer service gave a halfhearted non explanation for why they did it will definitely delete by the end of the year if im still blocked

scammers things are cheap but note that you will get zero support if the seller scams you use ebay instead similar pricing and much safer better support i opened a dispute because the aliexpress seller sent me completely the wrong item i included detailed photos of the item packaging both sides all tracking numbers details on what i should have been sent everything literally every piece of evidence that exists result no refund dont use this scam site

make shopping easier good work i love this app because it makes shopping much easier and has lots of promotions freeshiping and most importantly protects your investments it allows you to download pictures of the items you are interested in along with dimensions and sizes of products

i believe this company has come a long way since their beginning and they work very hard to make all of its shoppers satisfied and happy i use both this app and their website on my pc as both platforms offer benefits if ae can shorten their delivery times they will become larger than most online retailers thanks always aliexpress

thank goodness for seller taking his time to send all necessary updates files and instructions to finish install refund service on ali express seems to be non existent myself and friends of mine always get denied returns and refund on expensive items use at your own risk basically regardless of item price you are stuck with what you get

i love aliexpress yes you get what you pay for so use your head if it seems to good to be true it is there are true bargains to be found and stuff that goes straight in the bin i have never had any bother with the sellers who go out of thier way to keep customers happy of all the sketchy online shopping including ebay i recommend it to my family and friends no worries just use your brain still a great app just be conscious of travel and world issues still use it once a fortnight

loved the app 9510 had so many great products at bargain prices even without the sale only thing is that the tax isnt added on the shown price and any issueserror are always rectified with easy returnrefund depending on issue but again they are so minimal its really not an issue for me

very happy with the app saves you money if you dont mind waiting for it edit reducing to two stars because when sending messages through the app it is impossible to find a modified picture like the one that marks what is wrong with the product or part of it and the message center is impossible to find

i have probably bought about 50 items through this app in the main ive been pretty happy however if you do have an issue youre knackered aliexpress will basically refer you back to the seller who will give you the run around and then refer you back to aliexpress who say your buyer protection has expired really poor customer service aliexpress need to realise a bad experience will stop people using them

sellers are allowed to scam buyers now they give you false tracking info and also lose your items in us customs and then they wont refund you they also have ai customer service so you cant deal withchat with anyone who will resolve your problem they also do everything to avoid refunding your money i went right to my credit card company to start a chargeback on the purchase since aliexpress wont do it beware

amazing app full of wonderful sellers if you pay attention to picking the right items from the right shop youll be fine just make sure you read the reviews properly before buying so far i havent had a single problem and i always receive top quality products at amazing prices

there are crooks acting as legitimate sellers zero decent customer experience we are just a you pay for an item and they send you something different ordered shorts and received a hdmi cable instead raised a case with aliexpress and it was closed with no proof do yourself a favour if youre going to buy through this app video record the parcel and open it or good luck raising a dispute when you get screwed just a matter of time there are plenty more app options out there now

i ordered a wireless charger a type c cable and a car charger from aliexpress and i was pleasantly surprised by the fast delivery it took less than a week to arrive in ksa which is much faster than i expected the wireless charger has a very good built quality and material and it works well with my phone the type c cable is also ok but i havent tested the car charger yet because i ordered it as a spare one overall i am satisfied with my purchase and i think the products are worth the

i went to purchase a item that cost less then 20 and you wanted to charge me almost 50 for shipping thats a bit crazy dont you think im deleting this all anyone would be crazy to pay more for shipping then the item is worth and the more you get the higher the shipping gets

beware 1111 scams the prices are much higher dont waste you money warning high battery usage from this app more that demanding game i suspect that they mine crypto or move a lot of data about the app hard to find my liked items and the sellers arent very ethical about the items no easy way to find how to reach support the coin games are pointless the discounted items sometimes cost more than non discounted

its really good app however you need to know veracity of the products and the store they are really cheap theres good stuff in there but you need to pick carefully to not buy clone or weak things almost thing are from the factory himself so quality may be very random theres a lot of various products like exactly parts of electronics like other stuff the downside of the app its like i said they come from the other side of the world so maybe they are gon na take a while to come

i have ordered from aliexpress numerous times now some times u get great stuff some times u get some cheap bs that looks nothing like whats advertised but the worst part is at least 3 times my order has never been sent and ive had no choice but to cancel it if u r gon na let sellers on ur platform then u r responsible for them they shouldnt be allowed to offer a sale price and then never send the order so u have to go back and pay full price or so they think u will anyway

most of the items purchased break within a short period and its incredibly difficult to get a replacement only had negative experiences when shopping on this platform will use other vendors avoid at all costs

overall the app does what it is intended to do my only criticism is the marketing games for coins and i suspect that the developers of the app usually make those free mobile games most of the time and have missed the brief the games are the source of any nuisance whether a pop up or a notification and since its a marketingcatalogue app there should be the option to turn off the games and their respective notifications because its a catalogue not a free game

this app has its good side and it has its bad sides but ive received everything that ive ordered from this app some items were bad and some items were really good some items take forever to receive and some items came fast it all depends on the seller and make sure they have good reviews 8 out of 10 times the ones that have good reviews are the ones that you can count on receiving and getting a good product

generally the app is quite good one functionality could be added if the seller writes an enquiry it is visible within the app notifications but not in the buyers emails on his primaty email account which is a bit inconvenient and may cause delays in providing a reply best regards

very good app very good prices and shipping times very however some of the items are not as described and are pure junk so if youre prepared to lose a few dollars on a simple gamble go for it most items are pretty good

low cost and fast shipping to uk problem is the packaging is terrible and probably 65 of what i have bought has arrived damaged returns are easy but who can be bothered with that they are legit but i honestly wouldnt recommend ive given up with them

i have been shopping with ali express for a while now and all in all it has been a good experience the app is very easy to use deliveries are usually pretty quick the longest you will have to wait is around 1 month it really depends on how quickly the seller sends off the items that you ordered

never before had such a bad experience with an online retailer after placing my order they immediately canceled saying that the item was out of stock then held my funds for 20 days the purchase was expensive and meant to be a present so this was as inconvenient as it could have been first and last time placing an order with aliexpress

bait and switch scam i added a bunch of items to my cart for 99 cents and when i go to checkout all the items went up in price i contacted support but they refuse to correct it do not give these guys any money or credit card information untrustworthy

found what i was looking for put them in my cart and purchased from that point on tracking the transaction was so nonexistant i thought it didnt go through almost bought them twice however i purchased at the end of october and received them early november transaction tracking stated estimated delivery date of early january no other updates were made until they showed up on my porch i guess i should just count my blessings

the worst shop ive ever used in my life confusing coupons coupons that doesnt work or disappear a second later coins that arent really working spam from seller spam from app cheap or bad goods poor english in the descriptions of the goods really bad customer service where people cant speak cant understand what you really need

ordered stuff got most of it one item the seller im pretty sure isnt going to honor the sale great for low budget christmas shopping just make sure that the seller youre buying from has at least a 98≤ positive feedback before purchasing for context the seller still has a couple days to send it ill update you with a conclusion

i have ordered quite a few items with mixed results recently i ordered 2 heat pads more than 2 weeks after i placed the order the day before delivery was guaranteed the order was refunded no money lost but i lost 2 weeks and then had to order elsewhere seller did not find out after more than 2 weeks he had no stock i tried to raise an issue but because it didnt fit any standard complaints it wasnt possible to complain aliexpress isnt interested so i will stop using uninstall app

after a week with this app i can say it is an awesome app i ordered some things that came pretty quickly app is easy to use and also has shipping confirmation so youll always know your item will arrive although i didnt test the return feature of this app because items came as described i would recommend this app to anyone who wants to save a buck or two

over all app is good mostly items are cheap in rate but promotion rates are fake when you go for selection the price will be change there is no option for get together 1 order which contains from different sellers delivery upon the seller not on the orders which is difficult

well i am very impressed with the service from aliexpress the items were cheaper by far than if i had purchased them from my own country uk the speed of delivery is fantastic and tracking was updated regularly so i always knew where my parcel was i will definitely order more items many thanks

new 1star 0 customer protection service you basically are on your own and any wrong purchase is on you even if items clearly are advertised falsely to scam the buyer aliexpress only cares to take its fee and lets sellers do anything as long as they keep selling search got to be half fake and very inconvenient youre shoved items that clearly do not match your search old 5star very convenient lots and lots of products very cheap prices have space for little improvement

aliexpress has definitely stepped their game up ordered some stuff years back so i was aware of the long shipping times international shipping but recently went back on the app and ordered some stuff and their prices are unbeatable their clothes have always been solid and well made but my order shipped to my house in a week and a half which was insanely good time youve gained a customer

good app the only issue i face is that it keeps on changing the language country i am often locked out of my account and the app never sends verification code to login again i wish it was more user friendly
some great deals but some total ripoffs you always have to compare with other vendors sortingfiltering is pretty bad likely on purpose to show you something else you might end up buying

i bought a phone screen as original and after 03 days of installing it it completely stopped working to the point that i could not restart the phone it turned out to be fraudulent and this is according to the testimony of a phone repair professional i opened a dispute but unfortunately they gave the right to the cheating seller and i did not get my right back

love this app so much everyday you can get great stuff thar they offer their shoppers for a 199 usa dollars as long as you check out the things you picked first time is only 3 items allowed then you can get up to 10 items the next time for these low prices they have different fun games also you can play to earn coins towards your purchases overall i am very satisfied with this app thank you so much aliexpress your changing lives by helping us to afford the things we need these days
